    ResponseEntity
    Communicates the outcome of the RESTful operation submitted to the server, where ResponseEntity.getCode() has a numeric value that always maps back to a Result, and ResponseEntity.getMessage() contains the system assigned URN stored in IUrnNamespace.getUrn() or a detailed error message describing the failure.
    ResponseEntity.Builder
    Convenience method for quickly building a ResponseEntity.
